Steps to run this project: 

1. Open the terminal.
2. type "npm start" or "npm run server" which will run the server.js using nodemon.
    It will start the server and connect to mongodb.
3. For performing CRUD operations:
    > Open POSTMAN
    > GET Operation: Enter the URL: "http://localhost:3000/api/movieModel" to perform GET the movies added to the mongodb.
    > POST Operation: To add movies:
                Select POST
                Enter the URL: "http://localhost:3000/api/movieModel"
                Select Body > raw > JSON
                In the Body, enter movie data. 
                    Eg. {
	                          "name" : "Hate Story",
                          	"img" : "http", 
	                          "summary" : "data about movie"
                         
                        }
                Click on send.
    > PUSH Operation by using ID: To update the data
              Select PUSH
              Enter the URL: "http://localhost:3000/api/movieModel/movie_id_generated"
                    where movie_id_generated will be the _id Eg. "5ea958b1c6742e8d62549fd8"
              Select Body > raw > JSON
                In the Body, enter movie data. 
                    Eg. {
	                          "name" : "Hate Story",
                          	"img" : "http", 
	                          "summary" : "data about movie"
                         
                        }
                Click on send.
     > DELETE Operation by using ID: To delete record or movie.
               Select DELETE
               Enter the URL: "http://localhost:3000/api/movieModel/movie_id_generated"
                    where movie_id_generated will be the _id Eg. "5ea958b1c6742e8d62549fd8"
               Click on send.
              
4. To display the data on the web browser:
        Enter the URL: "http://localhost:3000/api/movieModel" or "http://localhost:3000"
              
	
    
